item.title: Ah! Please help
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

username is right - go into item.cfg and use “search” and look for names like thses:

abyssal_whip dragon_chainbody dragon_sq_shield dragon_plate_legs dragon_plate_skirt

Here also are some codes from the top of my head:

4151 (abyssal whip) 1038 (red partyhat) 1040 (yellow partyhat) 1042 (blue partyhat) 1044 (green partyhat) 1046 (purple partyhat) 1048 (white partyhat) 1050 (santa) 995 (coins)

Enjoy!

~Mod Taharok
